      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      private long connectionTimeout
      the maximum number of milliseconds that a client (that's you) will wait for a connection from the pool Default: 30000 (30 seconds) 客户端等待连接池连接的最大毫秒数
      private boolean enabled
      启用该连接池
      private long idleTimeout
      the maximum amount of time that a connection is allowed to sit idle in the pool Default: 600000 (10 minutes) 允许连接在连接池中空闲的最长时间(以毫秒为单位)
      private int maximumPoolSize
      the maximum size that the pool is allowed to reach, including both idle and in-use connections Default: 10 最大池大小
      private long maxLifetime
      the maximum lifetime of a connection in the pool Default: 1800000 (30 minutes) 池中连接关闭后的最长生命周期
      private long validationTimeout
      the maximum amount of time that a connection will be tested for aliveness.

      • enabled

        private boolean enabled
        启用该连接池

      • maximumPoolSize

        private int maximumPoolSize
        the maximum size that the pool is allowed to reach, including both idle and in-use connections Default: 10 最大池大小

      • maxLifetime

        private long maxLifetime
        the maximum lifetime of a connection in the pool Default: 1800000 (30 minutes) 池中连接关闭后的最长生命周期

      • connectionTimeout

        private long connectionTimeout
        the maximum number of milliseconds that a client (that's you) will wait for a connection from the pool Default: 30000 (30 seconds) 客户端等待连接池连接的最大毫秒数

      • idleTimeout

        private long idleTimeout
        the maximum amount of time that a connection is allowed to sit idle in the pool Default: 600000 (10 minutes) 允许连接在连接池中空闲的最长时间(以毫秒为单位)

      • validationTimeout

        private long validationTimeout
        the maximum amount of time that a connection will be tested for aliveness. This value must be less than the connectionTimeout. Lowest acceptable validation timeout is 250 ms. Default: 5000(5 seconds)

        连接将被测试活动的最大时间量
